  "terms": [
    "Temp Storage"
  ],
  "definition": "Short for \"temporary storage\". It's not a way to refer to a storage system that will only be used temporarily. It refers to a storage system in which boxes are stored temporarily, usually until a second box of the same item type reaches the system and they can be combined in a Merger and then be sent to a more final storage (like Bulk Storage, Chest Hall or others). See VBS002, VBS003, VBS004, and VBS006 for examples.",
